features: True Space Saver - In addition to the two-way zipper at the top, a zipper is fitted on the side of the packing cubes for travel. Once the side zipper is closed, the excess air will be expelled and the simple and convenient compression is complete. The compression cubes have been tested to save up to 50% of space!

Mesh Toiletry Bag - Are you always annoyed by the many small toiletries piled up in a bag and difficult to find the right items? In the compressible packing cubes set, there is a wrapped the toiletry bag with a fine, tear-resistant mesh fabric, so you can quickly find the right items through the mesh. No more worrying about not being able to find the right item to dampen your mood on the road!

Upgraded Cationic Polyester - We are sure that every customer wants a durable set of packing cubes compression, so we upgraded the fabric. These packing cubes for suitcases is made of cationic polyester, which is easy to clean, and has superb abrasion and tear resistance to withstand long time use. The fabric has a waterproof coating that prevents splashes of water from seeping into the fabric and wetting your clothes.

No Burden, More Convenient - The complete set of compressed packing cubes only 1.5 pounds but the cationic polyester is thick, and will hardly add extra weight to your luggage. The travel cubes for packing are equipped with sturdy, smooth metal two-way zippers, each with an extension cord to ensure quick and easy packing and unpacking every time. Each compression packing cube has a sturdy handle for easy grabbing and hanging while traveling.

Versatile Use - Because compressible packing cubes for travel come in a variety of sizes and are equipped with handle, you can pack them in backpacks, duffle bags, suitcases, or just carry them in your hand and use these compression cubes for packing on business trips, camping expeditions, and vacations. When you're not on the go, you can also use them as cabinet storage organizers to keep your closet organized and tidy.

Quality Guarantee - DIMJ aims to provide high quality products and thoughtful service to every customers.If there are any quality problems during use, please do not hesitate to contact us for a satisfactory answer!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for organizing suitcase
reviews.reviewText: As a well-organized individual, the Compression Packing Cubes by DIMJ are an absolute game-changer for my travel experiences. With their upgraded fabric and lightweight design, they offer unparalleled convenience and functionality. The 8-pack set, complete with a mesh toiletry bag, provides ample space for all my belongings while ensuring everything stays neatly organized within my suitcase. From separating clothing items to keeping toiletries in check, these packing cubes excel in streamlining my packing process. The grey and black color scheme adds a touch of sophistication to my luggage ensemble. Overall, these packing cubes are my go-to choice for maintaining order and efficiency during travel, making them an essential companion for any journey.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 14, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A very generous number of packing cubes, but maybe not the strongest or best made I've seen
reviews.reviewText: This is a really nice set of packing cubes. I was surprised by the number of cubes and variety of sizes you get with it. The designs are well thought out, I especially like that there is an external handle on each cube so that when they are in your suitcase, it's easy to grab hold of one and pull it out. Not all packing cubes I've tried have an external handle like that. The main downsides I found were that (1) the material does not feel like the strongest/highest quality material I've felt on other packing cubes and (2) some of the zippers are less-than-smooth to open and close. Mind you, neither of those negatives are things that would prevent me from using these; I'm just making note of it versus others I have tried. I have found it is never a good idea to severely overstuff a packing cube in hopes that it will magically flatten a mammoth stack of clothing. That's going to be especially true for this set; I do not think the zipper stitching would hold up to very much stress. However, if you pack clothing in these in a sensible way, they do nicely compress a reasonable amount of clothing. By virtue of the quantity of cubes you get and the variety of sizes, I think this is a great option to try out packing cubes. Overall, I'm pleased with this product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fantastic--will never leave home without these packing cubes!
reviews.reviewText: I got these for an international trip. I'd used packing cubes before, but never compression packing cubes. Switching to these is like going from a bicycle to a motorcycle! They are really well-made. All internal seams are fabric covered to prevent fraying and zipper snags. The zippers are all sturdy and zip smoothly. Best of all, they do exactly what they say and compress your clothing down by about 1/3rd (depending on fabric type). To demonstrate, I packed 3pairs of long-sleeved pajamas into one of the packing cubes, then did the compression zipper (see pictures). You will gain a ton of suitcase space with these! I'm not sure how wrinkled your belongings will be, so for my next trip I'm planning on not compressing my shirts and dresses cubes on the way out ( just the cubes with PJs, jeans, socks etc). Then, on the way back when I always manage to accumulate things and am in need of extra suitcase space, I'll compress all the cubes and gain an ton of space. With these compression packing cubes your suitcase will be akin to Dr. Who's spaceship--it will be bigger on the inside! Absolutely love these!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I've previously used the clear travel bags that you squeeze the air out of, so I was curious about these, since I have an upcoming trip to Australia and Malaysia in a month. When I ordered these, I didn't realize what a terrific variety of bags came in the set. It's a very clever system, using the same double-zipper idea used on some luggage. I'm not sure that they compress as much as the clear bags, but they are MUCH easier to use, since you open both zippers, fill the bag, then close the main zipper and then close the expansion area zipper, compacting your clothes in the process. I love the way these fit into my carry-on bag, stacked one on top of the other. I'll take an empty one with me as well, and move dirty clothes into that one.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good quality, nice looking travel cubes
reviews.reviewText: I have had friends give me glowing recommendations for using travel packing cubes. I have not used them yet, but I am looking forward to giving them a try and seeing if they are as big of a travel hack as they suggest they are. These are sturdy, made of quality materials and look nice. Upon inspection, I did not find any misses stitching or loose threads. The zippers worked well and they look like they will last a long time. They fit in a nice zippered carrying case so they can be stored and kept out of the way.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great assortment of sizes, sturdily made
reviews.reviewText: I really like the assorted sizes of packing cubes. In addition to the packing cubes there was a small laundry bag and a shoe bag. There is also a cool little bag that all the cubes and bags fit into when not in use.The packing cubes are made of a slightly heavier material than other cubes I've bought that advertise as ultralight. There are double zippers that allow the compression. The zippers are slim, nylon and flush against the material.There are two large bags, one medium and 2 smaller bags. I think this will be about enough to hold a week's worth of clothes.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for storage
reviews.reviewText: The compression packing cubes are not only for travel. I got them to help organize and keep our blankets clean and to store them behind our couch till we wanted one. I use the smaller ones for travel and other organizational needs. The material is very sturdy and waterproof. The zippers seem to be extra tough and zip with a very smooth closure. With the cubes completely unzipped you fill them 3/4 full with whatever you want then zip them completely around to compress the cube in less than half of what it started.
